title.en: Kirawaremono no "Hakuton Reijou" no Maki Modori. Nidome no Jinsei wa Shippai shimasen wa!
Enzai Reijou wa Shinjitai - Ginpatsu ga Fukitsu to Iwarete Konyaku Hakisareta Shishaku Reijou wa Ansatsu Kizoku ni Dekiaisarete Daini no Jinsei wo Tannou suru you desu
Sabaku no Kuni no Amefurashi Hime ~Zense de Shokei Sareta Mahoutsukai wa Nouka no Musume ni Narimashita~
Kirawaremono no Reijou wa, Watashi ga Aishimashou. ~Imasara Dekiai shite Kite mo, Mou Osoi desu!~
Shi ni Modori no Sachiusu Reijou, Konse de wa Saikyou Last Boss Ogikei-sama ni Dekiaisaretemasu
Koi ni Koisuru Koushaku Reijou no Kojirase Renai
Kono Ai wa, Kokuou Heika no Gomeirei Janai - Ohitori-sama Kibou no Reijou desu ga, Funaka na Kishi ga Hanashitekuremasen!
Doumo, Akuyaku ni Sareta Reijou desukeredo
Ochikobore Reijou wa, Koushaku Kakka kara no Dekiai ni Kizukanai ~Konyakusha ni Shimeisareta no wa Saishoku Kenbi no Ane de wa Naku, Watashi deshita~
Binbou Kishi ni Yomeiri Shita Hazu ga!? Yajin Reijou wa Koutaishihi ni Natte mo Ryuu wo Karitai
Royal Cinderella Mama: Tengai Kodoku no Botsuraku Reijou wa Reitetsu Koutei ni Dekiaisareru
Kinou made Namae mo Yonde Kurenakatta Koushaku-sama ga, Kyuu ni Dekiai shitekuru no desu ga?
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
